OL,3,CScale of workplace violence and abuse
OL,4,C'shocking and unacceptable', says
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FThe father of a woman killed by a
OL,8,Fformer colleague who stalked her has
OL,9,Fcalled for employers to do more to
OL,10,Fensure workplace safety after a survey
OL,11,Fsuggested almost a third of workers
OL,12,Fexperienced violence, aggression or
OL,13,Fabuse in the past year.
OL,15,FThe charity behind the research
OL,16,Fdescribed the findings as "shocking
OL,17,Fand unacceptable", as they called for
OL,18,F"stronger laws, better training, and a
OL,19,Fshift from a culture of tolerance to
OL,20,Fone of accountability" when it comes
OL,21,Fto workplace safety.
