OL,3,CScale of workplace violence and abuse
OL,4,C'shocking and unacceptable', says
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FThe Suzy Lamplugh Trust commissioned
OL,8,Fpolling that found that around one in
OL,9,Ffive workers (20%) feel at risk of
OL,10,Fviolence at work and almost a third
OL,11,F(31%) have experienced at least one
OL,12,Fincident in the past year.
OL,14,FThe most common behaviour was verbal
OL,15,Fabuse (21%), followed by bullying or
OL,16,Fintimidation (14%).
OL,18,FAround 3% of people had experienced
OL,19,Fphysical assault and the same
OL,20,Fpercentage said they had faced sexual
OL,21,Fharassment or assault.
