OL,4,C'shocking and unacceptable', says
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FSuky Bhaker, chief executive of the
OL,8,Ftrust, said, "Every statistic in this
OL,9,Freport represents a person who has
OL,10,Fexperienced violence or abuse or felt
OL,11,Funsafe, unsupported, and unheard at
OL,12,Fwork. The scale of violence against
OL,13,Ffrontline staff is both shocking and
OL,14,Funacceptable.
OL,16,F"Workplace violence is not inevitable
OL,17,Fand must be prevented. Our research
OL,18,Fshows what needs to change: stronger
OL,19,Flaws, better training, and a shift
OL,20,Ffrom a culture of tolerance to one of
OL,21,Faccountability.
